Extern

	Function C_UpdateNormals(no_tris:Int,no_verts:Int,tris:Short Ptr,vert_coords:Float Ptr,vert_norms:Float Ptr) ' used by TMesh.bmx

	Function C_NewMeshInfo:Byte Ptr()
